title: A man of newts and taste
author: VD
content_html: It being Wednesday, A Binge at Brinkley Episode 3: Sympathy for the Devil is now live at Webtoons. I like to think that Arkhaven is getting the hang of this new medium. And thanks to all the new subscribers, as we’re already about one-third of the way towards being able to fully support an entirely new monthly series.
